-- Spain says to define strategy to maximise return in Bankia
-- By Andres Gonzalez
-- Wed Jan 15, 2014 07:31AM EST
-- None



MADRID, Jan 15 (Reuters) - The Spanish authorities will define in the coming weeks and months what is the best strategy to maximise the state's return on its investment in bailed-out lender Bankia <BKIA.MC>, Economy Minister Luis de Guindos said on Wednesday.

